
SNAIL : Put a snail in your shell

   - Researchs and prints station's informations
   - Print next trains on a station

Usage : 
   
   0) Init the database :

   > snail init [URL]


   1) Researchs and prints station's informations :

   > snail station Rungis
   PRU  P. DE RUNGIS AEROP.                 
   RF   RUNGIS LA FR. 


   2) Print next trains on a station : 

   > snail train PRU
   GOTA  22:38  2  MONTIGNY BEAUCHAMP                 
   GOTA  23:08  2  MONTIGNY BEAUCHAMP                 
   GOTA  23:38  2  MONTIGNY BEAUCHAMP 

